      "_comment_phase_2_08": "Visual testing substrate shipped 2026-05-15 (Phase 2 / 08). Wraps laptop-hands HTTP service at HANDS_URL with HMAC over HANDS_SHARED_SECRET. Surfaces browser.* + android.* + ios.* (stubs) + visual.* recipe/regression tools. Reachable via ecodia-full proxy once registered server-side."
